  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-48 is-title1-48 is-title-bold\">「2024 AMC10/12 考前衝刺講座」</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-32 is-title1-32 is-title-bold is-upper\"><em><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">#申請回放請見本文最下方<br />\n#零元優惠報名按讚留言</span></em></h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:26px;\"><strong>獵豹數學召集人 AMC頂尖專家</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><br />\n宗翰老師為同學們分析AMC10/12的命題特色與特殊的解題秘技，精彩可期，千萬別錯過！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:26px;\"><strong>宗翰老師主講</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><br />\n台北時間：8/31(六)AM 10:00~12:00 直播講座</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:26px;\"><strong>《適合學生》</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><br />\n1. 國中資優生以高中科學班/數資班為目標<br />\n2. 高中生以頂尖大學熱門科系為目標<br />\n3. 中學生以考好AMC10/12為目標</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:26px;\"><strong>《再問AMC》</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><br />\n獵豹的孩子為何都要接受AMC的相關訓練！？<br />\n<br />\n1.為何許多自認數學很好的同學在AMC10/12鎩羽而歸<span style=\"font-size:24px;\">！？</span><br />\n2. AMC10/12要在短短的75分鐘內作答25道題，要獲高分可能嗎<span style=\"font-size:24px;\">！？</span><br />\n3. AMC10/12 的訓練與一般的數學競賽有何不同？（配速、作答取捨、速解、命題範圍/特色）<br />\n4.AMC10/12的深水區（P21-25)要如何準備？<br />\n5.AMC課程為何是中學生最值得的課外數學訓練？（對段考、學測、分科、二階筆試的助益）</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2024091503190287389-8ba019b1.jpg\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong>獵豹指導學生參與各級數學競賽，歷年成績輝煌！</strong><br />\n<br />\n曾獲IMO (奧林匹亞數學)2金1銀、APMO(亞太）金、CPGE（法國高等學院預科）榜首、TRML團體2金與個人賽滿分，AMC/AIME二十年，獲AMC8多次滿分、AMC10滿分、AMC12滿分、AIME滿分，以及多位入圍USAMO其中有超高總分295、271分入圍。<br />\n<br />\n獵豹老師歷年指導的優秀學生無數，有獲IPhO(奧林匹亞物理）金牌、IOI(奧林匹亞資訊）唯一滿分金…<br />\n<br />\n<strong>世界頂尖大學皆有獵豹學子身影:</strong><br />\nMIT, Harvard , Stanford, Princeton, Caltech, Oxford, Cambridge, CMU CS, Columbia , UChicago, UCB….</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:26px;\"><strong>《費用及報名方式》</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">定價：NT$1000</span><br />\n零元優惠(擇一)：<br />\n方案1. 按讚留言「AMC10+1」並完成公開分享三篇指定FB文<br />\n方案2. (限獵豹現役學生)：按讚留言「獵豹AMC10+1」並完成公開分享一篇指定FB文</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:26px;\"><strong>《報名表》</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><br />\n- 報名步驟：請務必完成填寫1,2步驟表單，方完成報名程序：<br />\n<br />\n1.新生請先填寫「TC01自填表-獵豹學生聯絡資料」(填過者不需填寫，可略過)<br />\n務必填寫Line ID，FB請填「顯示名稱」<br />\n<a attributionsrc=\"https://www.cheetahstem.com/privacy_sandbox/comet/register/source/?xt=AZVyPfHNVZuM7rlE2NPx-Iu92i9DNCnqoDbLWDgm0F2tryFotLODEnLEMZt5n4ca8qP8IJyqJW0W7diuEa8tzgTtU1oklLcRmVV_FaVz_g5W9TFDqPxPUs3KNGsBjJE6j_PVf6ZbyyOHmAmQeXAoLKSOrlqUwGCTTsr4vYzt1Vgs_RmkwfAt6QZ-9hcTFckYmeIWP95kskAgYofxsQuHwZnERp7Pf5bu2DKKmK3yUoNqD_Z38TVaGIF8gbaWiKsr1mJqRyT2bznYjUtjav3oElK1BqanocjMfQJ1KdDd3ZQ1bnmvyGTmib33cKXrjbI4UdXWSkpAOMNyIpVfS32XX-pA648GJMNIeGJYMCecZfeQExDOThlzkiLA1RWZl4jw0MJKt5VUXrEsdj2LgG-sNZWf3y7kdkxJVdJJLJdLux5BdVmrURfZHbjyMQbqoTWKCneUXFvIkeqN93NjHptmbZgLWxRYkiay69JThYSgd7UucaccQgHp5VqtHDcXNADQ3TBnLBZ7i4cfC9Sdf9pmukvmq4WDVPIfVJzbLs8GJZgixGRbLpifWJnM_yV40R8enhYIv_WxiU4U78rErztzLTHAQmnofETh_vzPxoEFgWSaLY5ebZcC9QOB7OS9yePBQM7n_mswZuYxRtt6eYmyTnGOAf_SPyiljc4oVn7flR-BjFXyMUzjcmfmQC1eE1IoK1OYmPPdeRwkT0QIpykngkFFlRYmgF7LCDlwcsGWdOYK1HT3BbyV6gxK2Z-uUdHzpQcdaYlkI42XBqcAsDLompaFoMgLYY8q_-ZV58CU1vFpGgRpQJGtSBAgFXDIyThvTqWg2gg98roF2bPKk44ig-Un87hhTSwqIbdA0MV7TwqTaOHFnaPqxbo02kV_XUZySlWXihVEED-GQkTIWbTUqhkLsEN2h7bTyaucr7C4qoQBQGruC7FNgFUk2Abw7wo6sSm3F7sQE9R8T4Sd8YX3cnr-YYLtNv7kCoZyo2_0sL-xF1_8FJQ9ZPEDzHMxiiLdZwgQreHNBb-rSfY4mPyXxqqWzaErrwHncOflN_5S2GC23tW6MGa21pldnsqe5